  "texts": [
    "Neural network properties, such as patterns of keyword co-occurrence, better anchor thought abilities like learning, memory, and inference.",
    "There are ties to marketing management activities such as target market analysis and maintaining client relationships.",
    "Using a co-occurrence analysis, determined which terms occurred most frequently.",
    "Graphic representation of the co-occurrence data reflects this with larger circles for more frequent occurrences.",
    "According to the findings, the most prevalent concepts shared by all co-occurrence networks were machine learning, AI, big data, data mining, and marketing."
  ]
